<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>New Task Assigned</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
    <table style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; background-color: #fff; border-radius: 5px;">
        <tr>
            <td style="text-align: center; padding: 20px 0;">
                <img src="https://img.freepik.com/premium-vector/white-clipboard-task-management-todo-check-list-efficient-work-project-plan-fast-progress-level-up-concept-assignment-exam-productivity-solution-icon-3d-vector-render-white-background_412828-739.jpg?w=2000" alt="Task Tracker Logo" width="150">
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 20px;">
                <h2>New Task Assigned</h2>
                <p>Dear <%= @user.name %>,</p>
                <p>You have been assigned a new task in Task Tracker.</p>
                <p>Please log in to Task Tracker to view and manage your tasks.</p>
                <p>If you have any questions or need assistance with this task, please don't hesitate to reach out to the task creator.</p>
                <p>Thank you for using Task Tracker!</p>
                <p>Best regards,<br>The Task Tracker Team</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="background-color: #007BFF; padding: 10px; text-align: center;">
                <p style="color: #fff; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">&copy; 2023 Task Tracker</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
